{"article_id":"BlwT5OTyJNcYTm48","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump called the House Democrats ' push for impeachment a \" lynching \" Tuesday","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"as he pushed Republicans to rally around him amid the inquiry .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Mr. Trump used the incendiary language","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"as he tested a new line of attack ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"reasoning","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that Democrats should be careful what they wish for","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"because he feels","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"they are watering down the standard for impeachment .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" So some day ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"if a Democrat becomes President","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and the Republicans win the House , even by a tiny margin ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"they can impeach the President ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"without due process or fairness or any legal rights , \"","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"he wrote .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"\" All Republicans must remember","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"what they are witnessing here","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"- a lynching .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"But we will WIN ! \"","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Washington observers winced at Mr. Trump ' s use of the word ,","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"since it evoked horrific crimes against black Americans in the U.S. South .","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"Rep. Barbara Lee , California Democrat , said","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"the comments exhibited ignorance","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"and will further harm Mr. Trump ' s standing with the black community .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"\" Of course , he has no understanding of this horrific history ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"I assume .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"And for him to say something like that was disgusting , \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Ms. Lee said .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"\" It hurts .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"It ' s painful ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"and he should apologize . \"","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Democratic leaders continued to condemn Mr. Trump through the morning ,","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"though said","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"they are not looking to formally rebuke him through a resolution .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"The Southern Poverty Law Center said","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s comment showed \" a complete disrespect \" for thousands of murdered black Americans ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"though the White House insisted","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Mr. Trump wasn ' t trying to draw comparisons .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" The president is not comparing what ' s happened to him with one of the darkest moments in American history .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"He ' s just not , \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"White House deputy press secretary Hogan Gidley said .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" What he ' s explaining clearly is the way","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"he ' s been treated by the media","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"since he announced for president . \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Some Capitol Hill lawmakers said","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"Mr. Trump should at least remove his online posting .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"\" You think","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"this impeachment is a LYNCHING ?","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"What the hell is wrong with you ? \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Rep. Bobby L. Rush , Illinois Democrat , tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"\" Do you know","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"how many people","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"who look like me","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"have been lynched , since the inception of this country , by people","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"who look like you .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Delete this tweet . \"","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"House Majority Whip James Clyburn , South Carolina Democrat","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"who is African American ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"the president \" has always been pretty loose with his words ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and this is another indication of that . \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"\" I really believe","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"this man is prone to inflammatory statements , \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"he told CNN ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"\" and that is one word","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that no president ought to apply to himself . \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Rep. Adam Kinzinger , Illinois Republican , urged Mr. Trump to retract his comment immediately ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"though Sen. Lindsey Graham , an ardent Trump supporter","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"who pushed back on the president ' s Syrian policy ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"the term was apt ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"according to multiple Capitol Hill reporters","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"who interviewed him .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" This is a lynching in every sense , \"","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"the South Carolina Republican said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":147,"left":91,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":75,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":80,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":76,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":4,"right":78,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":5,"right":77,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":85,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":84,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":